    - LSM: Separate idea of "major" LSM from "exclusive" LSM
    - apparmor: Remove SECURITY_APPARMOR_BOOTPARAM_VALUE
    - selinux: Remove SECURITY_SELINUX_BOOTPARAM_VALUE
