  * Cosmic update to v4.17.2 stable release (LP: #1779117)
    - crypto: chelsio - request to HW should wrap
    - blkdev_report_zones_ioctl(): Use vmalloc() to allocate large buffers
    - KVM: X86: Fix reserved bits check for MOV to CR3
